    <item>
      <title>美国北约大使谈援助乌克兰、结束战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-02/us-nato-ambassador-on-aid-for-ukraine-ending-the-war-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻北约大使朱丽安·史密斯表示，她谈到在乌克兰与俄罗斯交战期间继续向其提供货币和军事援助。她还谈到了盟国如何合作以及中国在冲突中的作用。她接受了彭博社的克里蒂·古普塔的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-02/us-nato-ambassador-on-aid-for-ukraine-ending-the-war-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:24:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Marex 称可可的极度短缺终于要结束了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/cooca-s-extreme-shortage-is-finally-set-to-end-marex-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大宗商品经纪商 Marex Group 称，全球最大种植区的可可产量复苏将结束导致今年可可价格飙升至历史最高水平的严重可可豆短缺局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/cooca-s-extreme-shortage-is-finally-set-to-end-marex-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:09:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透社称欧洲央行行长马赫卢夫预计今年只会再降息一次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/ecb-s-makhlouf-sees-only-one-more-rate-cut-this-year-reuters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社报道，欧洲央行管理委员会委员加布里埃尔·马赫卢夫表示，他愿意接受今年仅再降息一次，因为他需要更多时间来确信通胀率将达到 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/ecb-s-makhlouf-sees-only-one-more-rate-cut-this-year-reuters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:01:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以太坊 ETF 有望最早于 7 月中旬获批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/ether-etf-hopefuls-gear-up-for-sec-approval-as-soon-as-mid-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资产管理者乐观地认为，美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 将在 7 月中旬批准首批直接投资以太币的美国 ETF，并表示与监管机构的沟通仍然富有建设性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/ether-etf-hopefuls-gear-up-for-sec-approval-as-soon-as-mid-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 15:30:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
